@startuml US-09
title US-09 Developer Registration

actor Developer
boundary "Admin/Dev UI" as UI
control "DeveloperController" as DC
control "DeveloperService" as DS
database "DeveloperRepository" as DR

Developer -> UI: Enter developer name
UI -> DC: POST /developers {name}
DC -> DS: registerDeveloper(name)
DS -> DR: save(Developer{name})
DR --> DS: developerId
DS --> DC: success(developerId)
DC --> UI: 201 Created
UI --> Developer: Confirmation
@enduml
